# 🎓 Syrian English Tutor AI - Training Notebook

This notebook trains an AI tutor specifically for Syrian 12th grade English curriculum using a free Hugging Face model.

## 📚 Project Overview
- **Source**: Syrian 12th Grade English Textbook
- **Goal**: Create a conversational AI tutor
- **Model**: Fine-tuned language model for educational support
- **Platform**: Google Colab (Free Tier Compatible)

## 🎯 Features
- ✅ Vocabulary explanations
- ✅ Grammar assistance  
- ✅ Reading comprehension help
- ✅ Writing guidance
- ✅ Exam preparation
- ✅ Cultural context awareness